<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        {% include head.liquid %}
    </head>
    <body class="{{ bodyClass }}">
    <div class="page">
        <header>
            {% include header.liquid %}
        </header>
        <main>
            <div id="main-h1" class="main-h1-line"><ilw-content width="page">
            <h1>Donor Impact</h1>
            </ilw-content></div>

            {{ content }}
            <ilw-grid width="page">
                <ilw-statistic class="orange"><span slot="stat">$6.6M</span> Dollars raised</ilw-statistic>
                <ilw-statistic><span slot="stat">728</span> Number of donors</ilw-statistic>
                <ilw-statistic class="orange"><span slot="stat">$250K</span> General purpose gifts</ilw-statistic>
                <ilw-statistic><span slot="stat">1,270</span> Number of total gifts</ilw-statistic>
                <ilw-statistic class="orange"><span slot="stat">699</span> Gifts between $1-$100</ilw-statistic>
                <ilw-statistic><span slot="stat">181</span> Scholarship and fellowship recipients</ilw-statistic>
            </ilw-grid>

            <ilw-content width="page" id="pay-it-forward">
            <h2>Pay it Forward</h2>
            <p>Friends, donors, and alumni create lasting impact in the field of education by giving to priority initiatives of the College like these:</p>
            <ilw-columns gap="20px">
                <ilw-content class="donor">
                    <h3>Fund for Excellence</h3>
                    <p>This fund is used at the discretion of the Dean to support the most pressing needs of the College. These funds allow the Dean to address these needs in a timely manner and move forward initiatives identified throughout the academic year.</p>
                    <h3>Education at Illinois Scholarship Fund</h3>
                    <p>Gifts to this fund provide scholarships to students in the College of Education at the University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign.
                    <h3>Dr. James D. Anderson Fellowship in Education Fund</h3>
                    <p>This fund supports outstanding College of Education graduate students in their academic endeavors and provides opportunities for the worldâ€™s future leaders in education.</p>
                </ilw-content>
                <ilw-content class="donor">
                    <h3>Center for Culturally Responsive Evaluation and Assessment Gift Fund</h3>
                    <p>Gifts support the CREA conference, CREA research, and administrative costs in the Department of Strategic Initiatives and Specialized Programs in the College of Education.</p>
                    <h3>Youth Literature Festival Fund</h3>
                    <p>Donations provide unrestricted support of a biennial Youth Literature Festival organized by the Center for Education in Small Urban Communities within the College of Education.</p>
                    <ilw-spacer width="20px"></ilw-spacer>
                    <ul class="ilw-buttons">
                        <li><a href="https://uif.uillinois.edu/how-to-give">Invest in the Future of Education</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </ilw-content>
            </ilw-columns>

            {% include arrows.liquid %}
        </main>
        {% include footer.liquid %}
    </div>
    </body>
</html>